<item>
            <title>[LU-143] hash function of ldlm_namespace and lu_site is not good enough</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-143</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After turning on CFS_HASH_DEBUG_2, we can see hundreds or more traveling on list of these hash-tables if one single client create/stat/unlink millions of files under a single directory, which is bad for performance.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;ve worked out a patch to improve the hash function,  will post for review very soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
